Surf_nocturnal_final

FIXES:
-Added another vending machine to get guns faster
-Replaced the blockbullets wall with one that works on second platform
-No skipping map at spawn level
-ladder under jail to get back up from secret compartment

This is a night based map with a lengthy surf, vending machine five sevens, lasers in jail, and a secret one way wall which you can not be shot at in jail.

Comments are welcome

Enjoy!
--Buck
